"{\"uid\": \"themoscowtimes.com-2024-07-20-olympic-chiefs-say-russian-disinformation-inevitable-ahead-of-paris-games-a85776\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The International Olympic Committee (IOC) said Saturday it was resigned to the Paris Games being targeted by disinformation attacks following recent incidents blamed on Russia.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 176, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4, \"end\": 41, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 4, \"end\": 41, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 169, \"end\": 175, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999886400000344, \"rank\": 1.076011640234627e-05, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"IOC spokesman Mark Adams said he believed a campaign against the Paris Olympics was already under way as final preparations for the sports spectacular entered the home stretch.\", \"from\": 178, \"to\": 354, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 178, \"end\": 181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.361751280705807e-16, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 192, \"end\": 202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Adams_(basketball,_born_May_1956)\", \"score\": 0.5137413298825356, \"rank\": 0.45833333333342063, \"text\": \"Mark Adams\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Adams_(basketball,_born_May_1956)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Adams_(basketball,_born_May_1956)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Clearly there is a campaign of some sort going on,\\\" Adams told a press conference.\", \"from\": 356, \"to\": 439, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not the first or last time that the IOC will be targeted with misinformation.\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 524, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 483, \"end\": 486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.361751280705807e-16, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's getting more and more sophisticated.\", \"from\": 525, \"to\": 566, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am afraid it's one of those things that we have to live with\\u2026it's part of the divided world we live in.\\\"\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 675, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Adams was responding to a question concerning a feature-length fake documentary that emerged in 2023 titled \\\"Olympics has Fallen\\\" which used AI-generated audio to impersonate Hollywood star Tom Cruise.\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 878, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 852, \"end\": 861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999997259360873, \"rank\": 2.723811360820877e-07, \"text\": \"Hollywood\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 867, \"end\": 877, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The film, falsely purporting to be a Netflix documentary, was apparently designed to erode global support for the Olympics.\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 1003, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 917, \"end\": 924, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"score\": 0.9999999997528448, \"rank\": 1.305468004176195e-10, \"text\": \"Netflix\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier this year, the IOC said its President Thomas Bach was targeted by hoax phone calls from a group in Russia pretending to be representing the African Union Commission.\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1178, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1028, \"end\": 1031, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.361751280705807e-16, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1051, \"end\": 1062, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thomas Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\"}, {\"begin\": 1112, \"end\": 1118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999886400000344, \"rank\": 1.076011640234627e-05, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 1161, \"end\": 1166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999996226229798, \"rank\": 3.7468593903839766e-07, \"text\": \"Union\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"U.S. tech giant Microsoft's Threat Analysis Center meanwhile has said Russia has ramped up disinformation efforts against the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1318, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1196, \"end\": 1205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Microsoft\", \"score\": 0.9999656623999416, \"rank\": 3.182732366167109e-05, \"text\": \"Microsoft\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Microsoft\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Microsoft\"}, {\"begin\": 1250, \"end\": 1256, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999886400000344, \"rank\": 1.076011640234627e-05, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Russia has been barred from sending a formal team to compete at the Paris Olympics following the country's 2022 invasion of Ukraine.\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1452, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1320, \"end\": 1326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999886400000344, \"rank\": 1.076011640234627e-05, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 1444, \"end\": 1451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999429665250075, \"rank\": 5.701214377947927e-05, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, only a small handful of Russian athletes will be allowed to take part in the Olympics competing under a neutral banner.\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1582, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1487, \"end\": 1494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.5834537566069457, \"rank\": 0.6855712964192329, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A Message from The Moscow Times:  Dear readers,  We are facing unprecedented challenges.\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1672, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1599, \"end\": 1615, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Moscow Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Russia's Prosecutor General's Office has designated The Moscow Times as an \\\"undesirable\\\" organization, criminalizing our work and putting our staff at risk of prosecution.\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1844, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1673, \"end\": 1679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999886400000344, \"rank\": 1.076011640234627e-05, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 1682, \"end\": 1700, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor-General_of_Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999998726987168, \"rank\": 1.2730081335939088e-07, \"text\": \"Prosecutor General\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor-General_of_Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor-General_of_Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 1725, \"end\": 1741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Moscow Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This follows our earlier unjust labeling as a \\\"foreign agent.\\\"\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1907, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These actions are direct attempts to silence independent journalism in Russia.\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 1987, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1980, \"end\": 1986, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999886400000344, \"rank\": 1.076011640234627e-05, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The authorities claim our work \\\"discredits the decisions of the Russian leadership.\\\"\", \"from\": 1988, \"to\": 2072, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2052, \"end\": 2059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.5834537566069457, \"rank\": 0.6855712964192329, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We see things differently: we strive to provide accurate, unbiased reporting on Russia.\", \"from\": 2073, \"to\": 2160, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2153, \"end\": 2159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999886400000344, \"rank\": 1.076011640234627e-05, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We, the journalists of The Moscow Times, refuse to be silenced.\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2185, \"end\": 2201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Moscow Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But to continue our work,we need your help.\", \"from\": 2226, \"to\": 2269, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your support, no matter how small, makes a world of difference.\", \"from\": 2271, \"to\": 2334, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you can, please support us monthly starting from just$2.It's quick to set up, and every contribution makes a significant impact.\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2466, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By supporting The Moscow Times, you are defending open, independent journalism in the face of repression.\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2573, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2482, \"end\": 2498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Moscow Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Moscow_Times\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you for standing with us.\", \"from\": 2574, \"to\": 2605, \"entities\": []}]}"